  "title": "DELIVERY DRIVER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities including but not limited to:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Loading and unloading of goods .</li><li>Perform duties such as parcel deliveries.</li><li>Complete an allocated number of parcels daily.</li><li>Ensure goods are delivered in good condition without delay or damages.</li><li>Assist in loading and unloading of goods.</li><li>Ensure cleanliness and maintenance of the delivery vehicle.</li><li>Any other duties and responsibilities assigned from time to time</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Positive working attitude, responsible and flexible.</li><li>Self-disciplined and have the ability to work independently under tight deadlines in a fast-paced environment with relevant experience will have an added advantage</li></ul>",
